org.apache.flink.runtime.io.network.netty

类 SequenceNumberingViewReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.io.network.netty.SequenceNumberingViewReader
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    BufferAvailabilityListener

    class SequenceNumberingViewReader
extends java.lang.Object
implements BufferAvailabilityListener
    Simple wrapper for the partition readerQueue iterator, which increments a sequence number for each returned buffer and remembers the receiver ID.

    It also keeps track of available buffers and notifies the outbound handler about non-emptiness, similar to the LocalInputChannel.
